scene_desc:
1. Scene Overview: 
   The image depicts a multifunctional room combining a laundry area, workspace, and living space. The room is well-organized with a modern and clean aesthetic, featuring white cabinetry and furniture. A green rug adds a splash of color, and natural light enters through a window on the right.

2. Identified Objects:
   - Laundry Area:
     - Washing machine (bottom left)
     - Dryer (next to the washing machine)
     - Ironing board (right side, near the window)
     - Iron (on the counter above the washing machine)
   
   - Workspace:
     - White cabinets (upper section, spanning the width of the room)
     - Colorful thread spools (on shelves in the middle of the cabinets)
     - Books and binders (on shelves in the middle of the cabinets)
     - Desk lamp (on the desk, left side)
     - Sewing machine (on the desk, right side)
     - Black chair (in front of the desk)
     - Trash bins (under the desk, black and white)

   - Living Space:
     - White sofa (right side)
     - Cushions (on the sofa)
     - Blanket (draped over the sofa)
     - Coffee table (center, on the green rug)
     - Teapot and cups (on the coffee table)
     - Potted plant (on the coffee table)
     - Floor lamp (right side, near the window)
     - Potted plant (on the windowsill)

   - Decorative Elements:
     - Framed artwork (left wall)
     - Toys (on the floor, bottom left)
     - Slippers (on the floor, near the coffee table)
